<p><span>×</span></p>
</td>
<td class="wysiwyg-text-align-center" style="width: 59.6528px;">
<p><span>×</span></p>
</td>
<td class="wysiwyg-text-align-center" style="width: 80.1273px;">
<p><span>×</span></p>
</td>
<td class="wysiwyg-text-align-center" style="width: 60.7002px;">
<p><span>◯</span></p>
</td>
